	</tr>
	<tr>
		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" />RandomValue:
<br />   .dw $0000
<br />RandomVales:
<br />   .dw $0000,$0000
<br />RandomBytes:
<br />  .db $00,$00
<br />
<br />I am pretty sure that's how to do it.

		

		</td>
	</tr>
	</table>


	<hr width="85%" />

	<table width="85%" cellspacing="3" cellpadding="0" border="0" align="center">
