	</tr>
	<tr>
		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" /><strong>NAME = value</strong>   works fine with nesasm, and so does <strong>NAME EQU value</strong>  (note: no dot in front of EQU).

		

		</td>
	</tr>
	</table>


